# terminal-slide: HTML browser mode demo
Output assets/html-mode.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 400
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type "# HTML presentations open in your browser with auto-injected navigation"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "terminal-slide examples/interactive.html --port 9999"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Ctrl+C
Sleep 1s
